---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="BharatDCIM privacy policy. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your data."
>
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <span class="section-label">Legal</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Last updated: February 16, 2026</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section pt-0">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-lg prose-gray">
        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>
          BharatDCIM ("we", "our", "us") collects information you provide directly
          when you use our services, including:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Name, email address, company name, GSTIN, and contact details when you register or request a demo.</li>
          <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Data center consumption records, billing configurations, and tenant information you enter into the platform.</li>
          <li><strong>Communications:</strong> Messages sent through our contact form or email.</li>
          <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> Browser type, IP address, and device information collected automatically when you visit our website.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the collected information to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide, maintain, and improve our DCIM platform and billing services</li>
          <li>Calculate power tariffs and generate invoices on your behalf</li>
          <li>Respond to your inquiries and provide customer support</li>
          <li>Send relevant product updates and industry insights (with your consent)</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations, including GST regulations</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Data Storage and Security</h2>
        <p>
          Your data is stored on secure, encrypted servers. We implement industry-standard
          security measures including encryption in transit (TLS) and at rest. Access to
          customer data is restricted to authorized personnel only.
        </p>
        <p>
          Financial and billing data entered into BharatDCIM is treated as confidential.
          We do not share your consumption data, tenant information, or billing records
          with third parties unless required by law or with your explicit consent.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          We retain your data for as long as your account is active or as needed to provide
          services. Billing records and invoices are retained for a minimum of 8 years
          as required under Indian tax law (Income Tax Act, 1961 and GST Act, 2017).
        </p>
        <p>
          You may request deletion of your account and associated data at any time by
          contacting us at <a href="mailto:hello@bharatdcim.com">hello@bharatdcim.com</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Formspree:</strong> Contact form submissions</li>
          <li><strong>Google Fonts:</strong> Typography (Inter font family)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Each third-party service has its own privacy policy governing the use of your information.</p>

        <h2>6. Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          Our website uses minimal cookies for essential functionality only. We do not
          use third-party tracking cookies or advertising cookies. Session cookies are
          used to maintain your login state when using the dashboard.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Under applicable Indian data protection laws, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data (subject to legal retention requirements)</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent for marketing communications at any time</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of
          significant changes by posting a notice on our website or sending you an email.
        </p>

        <h2>9. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For privacy-related inquiries, contact us at:<br />
          <a href="mailto:hello@bharatdcim.com">hello@bharatdcim.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
